column5: Went out Sat Jan 20 at sunset for a couple hours.  Fish were biting.  Caught my personal best.  No electronics ... just jigging a foot or two off the bottom.  Approx 15ft depth.  Dinner was really good.
Those are some nice looking crappie! I haven't even had a chance to fish the kawarthas yet this year and I live on the darn lake.
damn those are some sweet slabs
Nice haul!  I wish I was out yesterday...
Good job, you gotta remember that spot for sure...
